nd to her representation in art accompanied by a lamb. The colloquial form <i>Annes</i> led to some confusion with <i>Ann(e)</i> in earlier centuries. Frequent in the medieval period, the name was revived in the 19th century, and has been especially popular in Scotland.  See also  Annis ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Agnes was born in 1400, in Lancing, Sussex, England, United Kingdom. She married John Goring before 1424, in England. They were the parents of at least 1 son. She died in 1460, in her hometown, at the age of 60."},"et":{"1400–1460":"1400–1460","1393–1450":"1393–1450","1424–1495":"1424–1495","before 1424":"enne 1424","1424":"1424","1400":"1400","1495":"1495","1450":"1450","1460":"1460","1393":"1393","about 1450":"umbes 1450","Burton with Coates, Sussex, England":"Burton with Coates, Sussex, England","England":"England","Lancing, Sussex, England, United Kingdom":"Lancing, Sussex, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1400–1460":"1400–1460","1393–1450":"1393–1450","1424–1495":"1424–1495","before 1424":"ennen vuotta 1424","1424":"1424","1400":"1400","1495":"1495","1450":"1450","1460":"1460","1393":"1393","about 1450":"noin 1450","Burton with Coates, Sussex, England":"Burton with Coates, Sussex, England","England":"England","Lancing, Sussex, England, United Kingdom":"Lancing, Sussex, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1400–1460":"1400–1460","1393–1450":"1393–1450","1424–1495":"1424–1495","before 1424":"avant 1424","1424":"1424","1400":"1400","1495":"1495","1450":"1450","1460":"1460","1393":"1393","about 1450":"environ 1450","Burton with Coates, Sussex, England":"Burton with Coates, Sussex, Angleterre","England":"Angleterre","Lancing, Sussex, England, United Kingdom":"Lancing, Sussex, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Agnes est née en 1400, à Lancing, Sussex, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Elle a épousé John Goring avant 1424, à Angleterre. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fils. Elle est décédée en 1460, dans sa ville natale, à l’âge de 60 ans."},"de":{"1400–1